


[{"content":"","date":"2026 5月 13","externalUrl":"https://ruusuge.top/posts/rsq/","permalink":"/zh-cn/posts/rsq/","section":"文章","summary":"","title":"ルースQ　解説\u0026結果発表","type":"posts"},{"content":"总有一天会写一点的\n","date":"2026 5月 13","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/zh-cn/posts/","section":"文章","summary":"","title":"文章","type":"posts"},{"content":"\n简单的自我介绍\r#\r2024年7月左右开始在全所为界隈进行活动。\n是中国人，目前居住在江西省南昌市。\n因为喜欢霜奶仙，所以将其用作自己的形象。\n名称的由来\r#\r早期以「Louis0213」的名义进行活动。\n转向全所为时使用了「ルース毛」作为名义。\n这个名义是为了模仿「ロン毛」，\n因为想不出来好名字所以做出来的造语。\n活动内容\r#\r使用FL Studio制作全所为界隈的模仿曲与重编曲。\n代理资料\r#\r绘：忘月\r友情链接\r#\r","date":"2026 5月 13","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/zh-cn/","section":"主页","summary":"","title":"主页","type":"page"},{"content":"\r文本\r预览\r生成\r放大:\r1x\r2x\r4x\r8x\r下载\r","date":"2026 5月 7","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/zh-cn/tools/cxxxii/","section":"工具","summary":"","title":"CXXXII 专辑封面生成器","type":"tools"},{"content":"不知道能干什么用的工具\n","date":"2026 5月 7","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/zh-cn/tools/","section":"工具","summary":"","title":"工具","type":"tools"},{"content":"","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/zh-cn/authors/","section":"Authors","summary":"","title":"Authors","type":"authors"},{"content":"","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/zh-cn/categories/","section":"Categories","summary":"","title":"Categories","type":"categories"},{"content":"","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/zh-cn/series/","section":"Series","summary":"","title":"Series","type":"series"},{"content":"","externalUrl":null,"permalink":"/zh-cn/tags/","section":"Tags","summary":"","title":"Tags","type":"tags"}]